<!doctype html>
<html lang="bg">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow">
  <title>Админ панелът е временно спрян</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      color-scheme: dark;
      --bg: #08090a;
      --panel: rgba(24, 26, 30, 0.94);
      --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      --gold: #d6a83d;
      --text: #f4efe6;
      --muted: #aaa59a;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 24px;
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.13), transparent 32rem),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #070809, #111317 52%, #08090a);
    }

    main {
      width: min(680px, 100%);
      padding: 28px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: var(--panel);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: clamp(28px, 6vw, 42px);
      line-height: 1.08;
    }

    p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
      display: inline-flex;
      margin-top: 22px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.35);
      border-radius: 12px;
      color: #f0cf77;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.08);
    }

    a:focus-visible {
      outline: 3px solid rgba(214, 168, 61, 0.45);
      outline-offset: 3px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <h1>Админ панелът е временно спрян</h1>
    <p>Статиите временно се управляват ръчно през проекта.</p>
    <a href="/">Към публичния сайт</a>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
